description.en: The Construction Resources (CR) Ontology is based on concepts and principles of construction project management to provide a centralized definitiopn of resources that can be used as shared entities with task planning and cost estimation for providing a unified context.

comment.undefined: This class is used for providing information about a construction resource.
The utilization rate of a (equipment) resource that is applied in a task.
The utilization factor of a resource that is applied in a cost item.
The quantity calculated from the geometrical element that is applied to the cost item and its unitary price.
